ArtyTorrent Pack 62-Ueberschall House Essentials Vocals 2-WAV

According to the licence, you need to give credit to the singers if you use these samples in a commercial release, so if you have a hit with something from this pack, you&#039;d better buy the CD and give a mention to Leroy and Fab, the vocalists involved.
